discipline military outfit

00:23:15.290 --> 00:23:17.880 align:middle line:84%
Richard I could rely
on at all times.

00:23:17.880 --> 00:23:20.330 align:middle line:90%


00:23:20.330 --> 00:23:23.670 align:middle line:84%
>>Whatever his many faults,
